RESTRICTED AREA
EMERGENCY MEDICAL CENTER

4
00:01:22,937 --> 00:01:27,609
<i>Severe side effects have emerged from</i>
<i>users with inflammatory skin conditions</i>

5
00:01:27,692 --> 00:01:30,069
